abstract: ITEMS.--The house of C. A. VAN ZANY, Jr., No 247 Clinton-street, was entered through the scatle Thursday night last, and robbed of property valued at $175. The family were absent in the country at the time, and the intruders were not interrupted in their operations....The body of an unknown man was found in the water, at the foot of Little-street, yesterday.
